HEADWORD: Firmless
<hw>Firm"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Detached from
substance.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Does passion still the <qex>firmless</qex> mind control?</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Infirm; unstable.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Firmless</xex>
